short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Displays expected Alaska Airlines EQM earnings on partner websites.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Trying to reach Alaska Airlines elite status faster?  Make a more informed choice when shopping for flights on Alaska Airlines' partners.  We show you the expected Elite Qualifying Miles (EQMs) earned from each itinerary, taking things like distance, fare classes, and more into account.  This Chrome extension seamlessly displays expected EQM earnings for Alaska Airlines' Mileage Plan when browsing partner airlines' websites.

Supported websites:
- American Airlines (aa.com)
- Finnair (US) (finnair.com)
- Singapore Airlines (singaporeair.com)


EQMs shown are only estimates for planning purposes and are not guarantees.
